<title>USA: FTP Software names Glenn Hazard CEO.</title>
<headline>FTP Software names Glenn Hazard CEO.</headline>
<dateline>ANDOVER, Mass. 1996-11-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>FTP Software Inc said Monday that it has appointed Chief Operating Officer Glenn Hazard as its chief executive officer.</p>
<p>Hazard joined the company in April.</p>
<p>FTP said David Zirkle, who has served as its chief executive officer since January 1993, will continue to serve as chairman of the board until he retires on April 1, 1997.  </p>
<p>After Hazard becomes chief executive, the chief operating officer position will be eliminated, company spokeswoman Suzanne Moran said.</p>
